<h4>Q: Skirmishers?</h4>
<p>The Kriegsspeil rules are suprisingly detailed in their treatment of Skirmishers, which allows for lots of separte Skirmisher action on the tabletop as the armies close with each other.</p>
<p>Most close order Infantry units can send out at least 1 skirmisher base each, by committing part of the 3rd rank, or by using integral Voltiguer Companies.</p>

